videos.headline: Oregon breaks through first on 20-yard TD run
videos.description: Tony Brooks-James takes it in from 20 yards out to give Oregon the early lead over Nebraska.

videos.headline: Ducks get creative on two-point conversion
videos.description: After Tony Brooks-James scores from 20 yards out, Oregon pulls out a trick play for the two-point conversion.

videos.headline: Armstrong hits Westerkamp for 22-yard TD for Nebraska
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong connects with Jordan Westerkamp over the middle for the 22-yard touchdown to cut Oregon's lead to 8-7.

videos.headline: Oregon RB Freeman leaves game with apparent injury
videos.description: Oregon RB Royce Freeman appears to injure his knee after banging legs with a Nebraska defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oregon RB Freeman leaves game with apparent injury) 2016/09/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: T. Brooks-James run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.description: Tony Brooks-James run for 2 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Lateral does not go how Nebraska intended
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong's lateral is too high for RB Mikale Wilbon to handle and Oregon recovers and returns it to midfield.

videos.headline: Nebraska can't stop Griffin on 50-yard TD run
videos.description: Taj Griffin scores from 50 yards out to give Oregon a 20-7 lead over Nebraska.

videos.headline: D. Pierson-El returns punt for 45 yds
videos.description: Ian Wheeler punt for 39 yds, De'Mornay Pierson-El returns for 45 yards to the Neb 19

videos.headline: Cornhuskers strike just before halftime
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong connects with Jordan Westerkamp for the second time in the game to cut the Oregon lead to 20-14.

videos.headline: Reimers climbs the ladder to give Cornhuskers lead
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong finds Bryan Reimers who makes the leaping grab, takes the hit and scores from 22 yards out to put the Cornhuskers in front.

videos.headline: Cornhuskers extend lead on 7-yard TD run
videos.description: Nebraska RB Devine Ozigbo scores from seven yards out to extend the Cornhuskers' lead to 28-20.

videos.headline: K. Benoit run for 41 yds for a TD
videos.description: Kani Benoit run for 41 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Nebraska QB Armstrong taken out with apparent injury
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong is taken out of the game after getting hit while running toward the sideline.

videos.headline: T. Brooks-James run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.description: Tony Brooks-James run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Armstrong's 34-yard TD run puts Nebraska in front
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong uses his speed to break through the Oregon defense to give the Cornhuskers a 35-32 lead.
